gamerules.wildRules: ON REELS 2 AND 4 WINS 5 FREE GAMES + EXPANDING WILD SUBSTITUTES FOR ALL SYMBOLS
gamerules.scatterRules: WHENEVER A SCATTER LAND ON THE SCREEN, THE PLAYER IS AWARDED A RANDOM MULTIPLIER THAT WILL APPEAR OVER THE BOXES.
gamerules.highestWin: Only the highest win pays perline
gamerules.fishingBonus1: When two wilds land together on Reel 2 & 4,Respin feature is triggered. During this feature, after the window evaluates, then the two wilds expand and cover reels 2 & 4. 5 respins are awarded, where the wilds stick to Reels 2 & 4 and the other 3 reels spin.
gamerules.fishingBonus3: Scatter Symbol Appears on reels 1, 3 & 5. Whenever a scatter land on the screen both during Base game and Free game, the player is awarded a random multiplier that will appear over the boxes. If more than one scatters land and award multipliers, then the sum of them will be given as a final prize.
